Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.6
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Concept D redesign for the stock iOS 16 Phone app, built for RootHide. Includes stable full-stage Favorites, Recents, Contacts and Keypad screens, inline contact details, in-app favorite selection, Siri/My Info My Card lookup, PhoneAura Studio and a RootHide PreferenceLoader pane.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
